{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"9a6df817-6674-4db9-a59b-e0e0a5359803","content":"Good news — with .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` **natively supports MTP**. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was a .NET 9 opt-in bridge and is **no longer needed**. You can simply remove it.\n\n`EnableMSTestRunner` is still required — it tells MSTest to produce an MTP-compatible executable.","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01L2tq8uR65jebU5X1U6zJDW","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_018p51hhiUeYoFwajMyye2Uw","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-4016100237174d8b976ddf665297df88/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-4016100237174d8b976ddf665297df88/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"5783a47e-2710-457e-8f0c-9ea0ef06c182","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about Microsoft Testing Platform (MTP) support. Let me provide accurate guidance.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` natively supports Microsoft Testing Platform (MTP) without needing the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property. Starting with .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` uses MTP by default when it detects an MTP-enabled test project (e.g., one with `EnableMSTestRunner`).\n\nSo:\n- `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` is no longer needed in .NET 10 — it was a bridge property for .NET 9 SDK to opt into MTP support in `dotnet test`.\n\n\n- `EnableMSTestRunner` is still required to generate the self-contained test executable through MTP, but since .NET 10 has native MTP integration in `dotnet test`, I can remove the bridge property from the project file.","outputTokens":557,"requestId":"0BD6:69BE5:48699D:54CFDF:69F00622"},"id":"86cfff70-e693-4555-94e7-e2e78f4c76dd","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:58:21.251Z","parentId":"e111bbe1-9e4f-4799-93db-ef2fd84e396a"}
